Package: weasel
Type: Package
Title: Wave-Based Extraction and Selection for Longitudinal Data
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R:
    person("Siard", "van den Bosch", , "siardvandenbosch@me.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Tools for selecting, filtering, and balancing longitudinal
    panel data across survey waves. Provides a scope-based pipeline for
    wave pattern analysis and a planning interface for scenario-based
    respondent selection with configurable missingness tolerances,
    interior-gap constraints, and endpoint requirements. Wave grids may
    be consecutive integers or the observed schedule (e.g. biennial
    panels). Includes tolerance-sensitivity and attrition-selectivity
    diagnostics, plus a generator of ready-to-paste methods-section
    justification text.
